latestPosts.caption:
MrBeast, along with fellow YouTubers Logan Paul and KSI, is making headlines in India as they launch their popular brands, Feastables and Prime, at Mumbai’s Jio World Drive Mall. This much-anticipated event on November 10 has attracted a huge amount of attention on social media, where fans are eagerly awaiting a chance to see the YouTube stars up close.

MrBeast’s Feastables chocolate brand and Logan and KSI’s Prime Hydration drink are both highly popular abroad, and their India debut marks a big step for both brands in tapping into the local market. Teasers from Prime’s official channels, asking “INDIA, ARE YOU READY?” have already sparked excitement, with fans and influencers sharing their anticipation online.
